        div {

          .button {
            font-size: 1em;
            padding: 10px;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid orange;
            border-radius: 20px/50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-out;
          }
          .button:hover {
            background: orange;
          }
          .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            transition: opacity 500ms;
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
            height: 578%;
            width: 117.5%;
          }
          .overlay:target {
            visibility: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            display:none;
          }
          .PopUp {
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 0px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            width: 60%;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 5s ease-in-out;
          }
          .PopUp .close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 30px;
            transition: all 200ms;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
          }
          .PopUp .close:hover {
            color: orange;
          }
          .PopUp .content {
            max-height: 117.5%;
            overflow: auto;
          }
